FCS_RBG_EXT.2.1,FCS_RBG_EXT.2.2.choice: The application perform all deterministic random bit generation (DRBG) services in accordance with NIST Special Publication 800-90A using Hash_DRBG. The deterministic RBG is seeded by an entropy source that accumulates entropy from a platform-based DRBG and a software-based noise source, with a minimum of 256 bits of entropy at least equal to the greatest security strength (according to NIST SP 800-57) of the keys and hashes that it will generate.

FCS_CKM.1.1(1).choice: The application generate asymmetric cryptographic keys in accordance with a specified cryptographic key generation algorithm RSA schemes using cryptographic key sizes of 2048-bit or greater.

FCS_COP.1.1(2).choice: The application perform cryptographic hashing services not in accordance with FCS_COP.1.1(2) and uses the cryptographic algorithm RC2/RC4/MD4/MD5.

FCS_COP.1.1(3).choice: The application perform cryptographic signature services (generation and verification) in accordance with a specified cryptographic algorithm RSA schemes using cryptographic key sizes of 2048-bit or greater.

FCS_HTTPS_EXT.1.1.choice: The application implement the HTTPS protocol that complies with RFC 2818.

FCS_HTTPS_EXT.1.2.choice: The application implement HTTPS using TLS.

FCS_HTTPS_EXT.1.3.choice: The application notify the user and not establish the connection or request application authorization to establish the connection if the peer certificate is deemed invalid.

FIA_X509_EXT.1.1.choice: The application invoked platform-provided functionality to validate certificates in accordance with the following rules: ['The certificate path must terminate with a trusted CA certificate'].

playstore_details.title: f0lio - Bitcoin & Cryptocurrency Portfolio
playstore_details.description:
f0lio is created to enable the every day cryptocurrency user to keep track of their altcoin portfolio in a beautifully designed, easy to use interface. 

The app allows the user to keep track of their crypto holdings held on virtually any exchange, monitor coin prices, view trends and keep up to date with market movements. All this in a colorful design, never seen before in a finance app.

BEAUTIFUL AND USER FRIENDLY
An interface that puts a smile on your face even when your portfolio lost some value. Keeping track of your finance doesn’t need to be boring nor ugly.  

PORTFOLIO OVERVIEW
Check your total portfolio value in all the major currencies (USD, GBP, EUR, BTC, ETH,...)  

ALL THE COINS
More than 2000 coins are already supported in f0lio: Bitcoin, Ethereum, Ripple, Litecoin, Steem, Dash, Zcash, Civic, Tezos, NEM, NEO, IOTA, Monero, Ethereum Classic, OmiseGO, SNT, Qtum, Iconomi, Dogecoin, Golem, Waves, Stellar, DigixDao and many more!

ALL THE CURRENCIES
All the currencies in the world are now supported in f0lio: COP,QAR,EGP,IDR,BGN,PEN,ILS,DKK,TZS,VND,MYR,UAH,SAR,SEK,HKD,AUD,CHF,KRW,VEF,HRK,CLP,THB,EUR,KZT,RUB,BRL,MAD,PLN,PHP,ZAR,USD,TWD,NGN,AED,GBP,CAD,PKR,JPY,HUF,KWD,BMD,SGD,CNY,TRY,NZD,ARS,RON,NOK,INR,MXN,CZK

ANY EXCHANGERS
f0lio supports and get the latest prices from all the exchangers: Coinbase, Kraken, Bitstamp, Poloniex, Bittrex, LocalBitcoins, Cexio, Bitfinex, BitSquare, Binance, Liqui, TheRockTrading, Gemini and many more!

KEEP TRACK OF OFF-EXCHANGE COINS
If you like to keep your coin in your local wallet (as we do!) you are still able to track all of them easily with f0lio. 

NEW COINS ADDED DAILY
Always up to date. 

COIN CHARTS AND WATCHES
Monitor the price and the charts of any coin on any exchanger. 

MARKET OVERVIEW
Always keep an eye on where the rest of the market is going. 

On our Roadmap:
• Store Coin purchase price and date so we can report profit
• Price alerts
• ICO alerts
• Import portfolio from exchanges

Get in touch: 
Website: https://f0l.io
Facebook: https://fb.me/f0lio
Twitter: https://twitter.com/_f0lio
Telegram: https://t.me/f0lio
Email: feedback@f0l.io
